<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">This is an excellent book and is based on the author&apos;s family history. I have read many books on this topic, both fiction and non-fiction, and found i<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">This is an excellent book and is based on the author's family history. I have read many books on this topic, both fiction and non-fiction, and found it very accurate. It was a little confusing to keep track of each family member and how they connected, but overall very emotional and realistic portrayal of what families went through during this time period.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
