        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1907070892" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8425703602511711052">What a fantastic debut novel! How the Kurc family survived the atrocities of WWII is an amazing true story of courage &amp; determination. The thing that stood out to me about this novel was that the experiences of the members of this one family were so diverse. Only complaint was that being a large family it was difficult trying to keep track of who, when and where everyone was. I did notice, however, that the print version includes a character chart which would&apos;ve helped out a lot. This is another</span>
  <span id="freeText8425703602511711052" style="display:none">What a fantastic debut novel! How the Kurc family survived the atrocities of WWII is an amazing true story of courage &amp; determination. The thing that stood out to me about this novel was that the experiences of the members of this one family were so diverse. Only complaint was that being a large family it was difficult trying to keep track of who, when and where everyone was. I did notice, however, that the print version includes a character chart which would've helped out a lot. This is another, absolute, must read for lovers of WWII fiction. 4.5 stars.</span>
